<div class="section">
    <h2>About the 2025 ABDC Review</h2>

    <p>
        The 2025 ABDC Journal Quality List represents the first full evaluation since 2019. 
        It integrates peer assessment with international journal metrics to ensure the identification 
        of high-quality publication outlets.
    </p>

    <p>
        The review includes journal additions, removals, ranking revisions, and classification updates. 
        Expert panels evaluated journals based on relevance, quality, and contribution to business research.
    </p>

    <ul>
        <li>Revision of journal rankings</li>
        <li>Inclusion of new interdisciplinary journals</li>
        <li>Removal of low-quality or predatory journals</li>
        <li>Updates to FoR classifications</li>
    </ul>

